From: Alexandru Avadanii <Alexandru.Avadanii@enea.com>
Date: Wed, 13 Jul 2016 21:29:22 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] kernel-flavor: linux-image-generic-lts-xenial

Ubuntu arm64: switch from using kernel 4.2 for Trusty
(linux-image-generic-lts-trusty) to kernel 4.4 backported from Xenial
(linux-image-generic-lts-xenial).

Signed-off-by: Alexandru Avadanii <Alexandru.Avadanii@enea.com>
---
 .../fuel_bootstrap_cli/fuel_bootstrap/settings.yaml.sample            | 2 +-
 fuel_agent/drivers/nailgun.py                                         | 4 ++--
 fuel_agent/tests/test_nailgun_build_image.py                          | 4 ++--
 3 files changed, 5 insertions(+), 5 deletions(-)

diff --git a/contrib/fuel_bootstrap/fuel_bootstrap_cli/fuel_bootstrap/settings.yaml.sample b/contrib/fuel_bootstrap/fuel_bootstrap_cli/fuel_bootstrap/settings.yaml.sample
index e1a2fc2..d6b766f 100644
--- a/contrib/fuel_bootstrap/fuel_bootstrap_cli/fuel_bootstrap/settings.yaml.sample
+++ b/contrib/fuel_bootstrap/fuel_bootstrap_cli/fuel_bootstrap/settings.yaml.sample
@@ -17,7 +17,7 @@ extra_dirs:
 # Save generated bootstrap container to
 output_dir: /tmp/
 # Defines kernel version
-kernel_flavor: linux-image-generic-lts-trusty
+kernel_flavor: linux-image-generic-lts-xenial
 # Define packages list
 packages:
   - fuel-agent
diff --git a/fuel_agent/drivers/nailgun.py b/fuel_agent/drivers/nailgun.py
index 5ff1cf6..1463f22 100644
--- a/fuel_agent/drivers/nailgun.py
+++ b/fuel_agent/drivers/nailgun.py
@@ -734,8 +734,8 @@ class NailgunBuildImage(BaseDataDriver):
         "i40e-dkms",
         "linux-firmware",
         "linux-firmware-nonfree",
-        "linux-headers-generic-lts-trusty",
-        "linux-image-generic-lts-trusty",
+        "linux-headers-generic-lts-xenial",
+        "linux-image-generic-lts-xenial",
         "lvm2",
         "mcollective",
         "mdadm",
diff --git a/fuel_agent/tests/test_nailgun_build_image.py b/fuel_agent/tests/test_nailgun_build_image.py
index 826e6a9..684bbfd 100644
--- a/fuel_agent/tests/test_nailgun_build_image.py
+++ b/fuel_agent/tests/test_nailgun_build_image.py
@@ -40,8 +40,8 @@ DEFAULT_TRUSTY_PACKAGES = [
     "i40e-dkms",
     "linux-firmware",
     "linux-firmware-nonfree",
-    "linux-headers-generic-lts-trusty",
-    "linux-image-generic-lts-trusty",
+    "linux-headers-generic-lts-xenial",
+    "linux-image-generic-lts-xenial",
     "lvm2",
     "mcollective",
     "mdadm",
